{"tid":1633980,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"仲記得和勇同行既就入黎","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:46:39.000Z","uid":32731,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a00e3f7528145a5918e1f03b46d171caf505da46","tid":1633980,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:01:19.000Z","msg":"革命係持久戰<br />\n無可否認而家勇武行得太快 和理非跟唔切<br />\n唔好唔記得和理非係其中一個抗爭手段<br />\n呢個手段係比國際睇 亦係比淺黃睇<br />\n點解人權法進程去得咁快 因為我地行動有理由<br />\n亦做成我地係弱者 被壓迫下去反抗既畫面<br />\n<br />\n我地裝修左咁多日 呢個進步值得鼓掌<br />\n但係對家係比緊陷阱我地踩 10.4製造無警時段<br />\n等你地班暴徒去破壞 被仇恨支配 亦會被臥底帶領行動<br />\n商家佬亦配合政府自己實行戒嚴 營造恐怖氣氛<br />\n目的都係比外國睇 香港暴徒而家無差別攻擊 搞到唔關事既都要落閘 當然我地香港人知道得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n所以我地呢家要做既係 比和理非進場<br />\n唱歌 摺紙鶴等等 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">亦係比時間文宣組做野</span><br />\n所以麻煩勇武暫停一下行動先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好次上次百七萬人咁<br />\n呢家最重要戰線係人權法 睇得出對家係好撚驚！<br />\n因為對家既所作所為都係比國際睇<br />\n千奇唔好中伏"},{"pid":"aefb79fcc84a9cd40820bb001d53ed910d5d96a7","tid":1633980,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:02:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632540\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632540</a><br />\n另加巴打高質長文分折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffd3e99fb5ccd1de588127e76805a26cddecdca","tid":1633980,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be55c86afabd9c2a92da1cdca559509eb9810cc","tid":1633980,"uid":223765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:03:46.000Z","msg":"文宣好緊要 唔知各區商場有冇開 希望聚到人"},{"pid":"6ae43ca28d028a3756153b13d35b847b3f35dece","tid":1633980,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:04:15.000Z","msg":"罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但和勇合一係成場運動既關鍵，兩樣一齊做唔撚得？講緊既係，拆鐵係唔撚會影響人權法，或所謂既民意，但對政權、運動係現時有最大既影響力"},{"pid":"a66104e2b2778dc89ea9510889fba2f2d86ea902","tid":1633980,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e74be7098e798f4ace3dcf07ecf4bfdab6e815","tid":1633980,"uid":86591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:07:24.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"44cc759fa11c717531a74b5e4f4fe823ac0413b7","tid":1633980,"uid":86591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a4df1622011fd6541528fbf9d37a4f2afe51d9","tid":1633980,"uid":86591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d7a31dc9a9d1558983ca37b00c25d6bc9b3a6a1","tid":1633980,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:08:13.0